.TH RAILGUN 1 "June 2026" "railgun 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
railgun \- scaffold DDD projects and integrations
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B railgun
[\fBinit\fR]
.br
.B railgun add context
\fIName\fR
.br
.B railgun add
\fIexpress|npm|renovate\fR
.br
.B railgun help\fR
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B railgun
initializes TypeScript DDD projects using @haskou/ddd-kernel, @haskou/value-objects and @haskou/eslint-config, and can add generated contexts and common integrations.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B init
Ask Linux-style questions with defaults and create a project skeleton in the current directory.
.TP
.B add context Name
Create a DDD context with aggregate root, id value object, repository, domain service, use cases, dummy repository and ObjectMother tests.
.TP
.B add express
Add Express support, a health route and ExpressKernelServer bootstrap.
.TP
.B add npm
Add GitHub Actions npm CI workflow and README badge.
.TP
.B add renovate
Add Renovate config and README badge.
.TP
.B help
Show command help.
